attributes.Long form description: The student tries to assemble the table to the legs, but the instructor tells him that it is better to assemble the shelf part. The student then attaches the shelf to the four legs one by one. Subsequently, the student grabs the table and screws each corner to the legs. Finally, the student stands the table on the workbench.
